          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">See that the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Start-Velocity</text><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> is always equal to the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">End-Velocity.</text></para>
        </td>
