    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Example continued...</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Interface2"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">VELOCITY DIS-CONTINUITY</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Definition of dis-continuity</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">:</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true"> the motion-value of the motion-derivative changes instantly, with a step. A Dis-continuity is also called a </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Step-Change</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">discontinuity</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> in </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> is </text><text styleclass="Interface2" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">not</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> recommended, of course. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">discontinuity in Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> is also </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">infinite acceleration</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> - mechanically impossible.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">discontinuity</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> puts a </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">kink</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">in the</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> graph.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">An example of a Velocity Dis-Continuity.</text></para>
